column2: As a customer, I can register as a member.
column14:
Registration includes the following data:
1) Username
2) Password
3) Email Address
4) Telephone Number
5) Address

column2: As an admin, I can login to the system.
column14: Admin required to use appointed username and password to login to the system.

column2: As an admin, I can add new driver.
column14:
Driver requires the following data:
1) Plate Number
2) Name
3) Identification Card Number
4) Car Type

column2: As a member, I can edit my information.
column14:
The information that can be edit are the following data:
1) Password
2) Address
3) Telephone Number

column2: As a member, I can send notification to customer.
column14: Driver can send notification to customer to notify them.

column2: As a member, I can know the real taxi fare.
column14: Member can know the calculated real taxi fare.

column2: As a member, I can do payment.
column14: Member can make payment for taxi reservation.

column2: As a member, I can select taxi driver.
column14: Member can select desired taxi driver.

column2: As a member, I can know the estimated duration.
column14: Member can view the estimated duration of journey.

column2: As a member, I can know the estimated price.
column14: Member can view estimated price of the reservation.

column2: As a member, I can view my reservation history.
column14: Member can view taxi reservation history.

column2: As a member, I can make a reservation.
column14: Member can make reservation by selecting driver, time, date, destination address and pickup address.
